suggested.document:
From storm damage roof repairs to maintenance and new installations, we specialize in residential roofing services.
	Roof inspections. You can trust our team to carefully inspect your roof for signs of damage and recommend a plan of action for moving forward.
	Roof replacement. We can remove your old roof and install a new roof in your choice of color and style using materials from the best roofing manufacturers.






	Our ServicesContact Us





Contact Our Roofing Company Today




Get a complimentary inspection and estimate with Barringer Brothers Roofing for all your roofing needs. Contact our roofing company today at (618) 703-3036 or use our online contact form to request your free estimate.
